        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>At the Hashemite Training Center, we are dedicated to providing a platform that connects students with field training opportunities tailored to their specialties, GPA, and geographical preferences. By simplifying the process of finding and applying for relevant opportunities, we empower students to build the skills and confidence needed to transition smoothly into their careers.</p>

