        </ul>

        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>We offer an all-in-one platform designed to simplify the field training experience:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>User-Centered Design:</strong> Our platform is designed with the needs of students in mind, making it easy to find and apply for training opportunities.</li>
